ng.<br></li><li>Environmental destruction.<br></li><li>Multiple platforming abilities including a grappling hook, jetpack, and <strong><i>SLAM</i></strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/c0ff5192f9a981d2eeb4e1b9643471c3.webp?t=1749017770\" width=420 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/6db0a8b5e021653786cc0d482252e789.poster.avif?t=1749017770\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/6db0a8b5e021653786cc0d482252e789.webm?t=1749017770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/6db0a8b5e021653786cc0d482252e789.mp4?t=1749017770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/bde22a0b7ad9e36d0f649d07f5fde962.avif?t=1749017770\" width=459 height=105 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008520/extras/4ec4df5ab9fb42621969b16a30315849.avif?t=1749017770\" width=500 height=281 /></span>",
